defs.name: enabled_quote
defs.docs:
Allow quote (" or ') in value
 For example
 ```ini
 [Section]
 Key1="Quoted value"
 Key2='Single Quote' with extra value
 ```

attributes.value: / In this example, Value of `Key1` is `Quoted value`,
/ and value of `Key2` is `Single Quote with extra value`

defs.name: enabled_escape
defs.docs:
Interpret `\` as an escape character
 For example
 ```ini
 [Section]
 Key1=C:\Windows
 ```

attributes.value: / If `enabled_escape` is true, then the value of `Key` will become `C:Windows` (`\W` equals to `W`).
